Compliation procedures:

1) download the package from sphnix site
2) tar xzvf sphinx-2.2.1-beta.tar.gz
3) cd sphinx
4) ./configure --prefix=/usr/local/sphinx
5) make
6) make install

Installation:

1)sudo add-apt-repository ppa:builds/sphinxsearch-daily
2)sudo apt-get update
3)sudo apt-get install sphinxsearch
 

To start/stop
sudo service sphinxsearch start



